reviewText: I ordered this vol of Taboo Charming Mother as fast as  I could for I knew a good deal of the story but not everything. I watched this vol and loved it. The animation is good but to me this is a classic H-Series. It was hard to find the other volumes at least one's with a worthy price for just one. In this vol her stepson and herself finally get truly get together and things begin to unravel even further when her sister is about to come over. Product arrived fast and came with no damage. Awesome H-Series.
